## ğŸ› Troubleshooting:

### Problem: Port already in use
```bash
streamlit run calmnow_app.py --server.port 8502
```

### Problem: Module not found
```bash
pip install --upgrade streamlit pandas
```

### Problem: Can't see butterflies animation
- Make sure you're using a modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
- The butterflies are CSS animations and should work automatically

