## ğŸ¨ Customization (Optional):

### Change Login Page Color:
In the code, find this line (around line 20):
```python
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFB6D9 0%, #FFC8DD 50%, #FFE5EC 100%);
```
Replace with your preferred colors!

### Add More Quotes:
Find the STRESS_QUOTES, CALM_QUOTES, or QUOTES arrays and add your own!

